{"tid":361324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一日三跳] 平田邨女子墮樓分屍","createTime":"2017-08-16T04:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T05:26:48.000Z","uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0f1bcce7d956b3d4627428a3342bf47637ef81","tid":361324,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"早上約7時49分，藍田平田邨平仁樓，一名中年女子從高處墮下，猛撞大廈外牆，再倒臥天井，當場分屍斃命。保安員發現後報警，消防及救護員到場，證實事主已經死亡。警方調查後得悉，死者姓施，51歲，現場未有撿獲遺書，初步相信事主由天台墮下，事件沒有可疑。據了解，她有情緒病紀錄。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170816/57086599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170816%2F57086599&d=MmY%2BrEgLL5rawwX1UuTFPZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2d8a3e74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170816%2F57086599&h=b12f4c66\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170816/57086599</a><br />\n<br />\n生係香港 的確係福氣"},{"pid":"a9facf89750a3a1fea68f3723c39c0e625df9542","tid":361324,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"774af23e2d44b82857ab622b1dfaf9cc5842bc40","tid":361324,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:26:48.000Z","msg":"日經"}]}